Question: The sole baboon in the image is eating a piece of fruit

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many baboons are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many baboons are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the baboon eating a piece of fruit?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the baboon eating a piece of fruit?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
